snippet.title: Yttr Trailer — Fabric/Quilt 1.18/1.19 Minecraft Mod
snippet.description:
Yttr is an expansive mod for Fabric & Quilt 1.18.2/1.19.2, sort of existing as a love letter to 1.4-1.6 modded. It contains fresh takes on a lot of common features, interesting worldgen, custom music, and all-new mechanics.

https://unascribed.com/yttr/

CurseForge: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/yttr
Modrinth: https://modrinth.com/mod/yttr
Discord: https://unascribed.com/discord
Soundtrack: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL9NJOGs_EhnOUqmoPf4uqWhe_02v-AFB4

All footage recorded by me and edited in Kdenlive. Actual in-game footage. Some sections are sped up.

Also on PeerTube: https://tube.sleeping.town/w/h67BoBWWy3F81wJTk1tSGp

0:00 Intro
0:10 Interesting Crafting
0:22 Horrifying Abominations
0:42 Breaking Bedrock
0:52 Fast Travel
1:07 Forgotten Wreckage
1:16 A Complete Overhaul of the Nether Ceiling
1:30 Useful Equipment
1:44 And Yet More Still
1:54 Outro
